        <mxCell id="7ujJaLgyB3FPEBS25mQC-12" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;align=left;spacing=12;dashed=1;dashPattern=8 8;" value="&lt;b&gt;What distinguishes Generative AI from ML, DL?&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;Generative AI goes beyond traditional machine learning. Instead of only analyzing data or recognizing patterns, generative AI systems also actively create new data that is similar to what they’ve learned from vast datasets, drawing from patterns within those data to produce something new." vertex="1">
